.git/
.github/
.venv/
# Exclude the test tree from the build context EXCEPT tests/scenarios/, which
# the runtime image ships so the frozen-scenario replay / measurement path can
# run inside the container (see Dockerfile: COPY tests/scenarios/). Use
# `tests/*` (not `tests/`) so the directory stays traversable and the
# re-include exception below actually applies.
tests/*
!tests/scenarios/
docs/
site/
infra/
console/
ui/
mocks/
examples/
tools/
scripts/
# alembic migrations ARE shipped in the runtime image so a one-off
# Container Apps Job can run `alembic upgrade head` against the state
# store (see Dockerfile runtime stage). Do not exclude them.
*.md
!/rule-catalog/README.md
!/policies/README.md
!/README.md
.terraform/
*.tfstate*
*.tfvars
*.tfplan
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
